    62921 [label="HitachiOpenLicense:\nSource is software source code, documentation sources, configuration files, and\nother files suitable for making changes. Object - a file resulting from a\nmechanical transformation of the source, such as compiled object code, generated\ndocumentation, or other media conversions. Sublicense\" means that the person who\nhas been granted this license re-grants the license granted to a third party. A\nlegal entity is an association of actors and all others who control them, are\ncontrolled by them, or are under their common control. The term \"control\" in\nthis definition refers to one of the following (1) directly or indirectly direct\nor indirectly direct and manage the corporation by contract or other means; (2)\nown 50% or more of the corporation's stock; or (3) have a beneficial ownership\ninterest in the corporation."
          ,fillcolor="beige;1"
          ,shape=plaintext];
    62922 [label="HitachiOpenLicense:\nhttp://www.imagemagick.org/script/license.php"
